<dl id="n40130c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40130c">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40130c"> 130(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Verrine </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: A verrine is originally a small thick-glass container with no base, which purpose is to contain a solid or liquid dish (starter, course or dessert), rather than a drink. </mm> </dd></dl>
